\frametitle{通信方案设计}
ROS 系统的两种通信方式 Topic 和 Service 均要求通信双方为 Node 类型；
        Node 在 Package 下，故第一步创建了一个 Package：

        \texttt{catkin\_create\_pkg ros\_langchain\_node roscpp rospy std\_msgs geometry\_msgs}

        然后生成如下目录结构：

        \begin{center}
        \begin{forest}
            for tree={
                s sep=5pt,
                font=\ttfamily\small,
                grow'=0,
                child anchor=west,
                parent anchor=south,
                anchor=west,
                calign=first,
                edge path={
                    \noexpand\path [draw, \forestoption{edge}]
                    (!u.south west) +(5pt,0) |- (.child anchor)\forestoption{edge label};
                },
                before typesetting nodes={
                    if n=1
                        {insert before={[,phantom]}}
                        {}
                },
                fit=band,
                before computing xy={
                    l=15pt,
                }
            }
            [ros\_langchain\_node/
                [CMakeLists.txt]
                [include/
                    [ros\_langchain\_node/]
                ]
                [package.xml]
                [src/]
            ]
        \end{forest}
        \end{center}

